textBox.richText: Skiing with Max, Gunter, Alli, and the Stephens’

Last day of xmas break. Started off the day with Max, Gunter, and Alli...hit the park. Quickly devolved to me and Max trying to find Gunter (doing drills from the lesson with Jay). That pretty much sums up the “part 1” video. Then, Part 2. Meet Rod, Michelle, Ken, and Amy at Snoasis. Okay, maybe not meet...ambush. Do a bunch of tree runs. Fun!
